\c 11 Soromoni unotsauka panzira dzaJehovha 1 Zvino mambo Soromoni wakanga achida vakadzi vazhinji vatorwa pamwechete nomukunda waFarao, vakadzi vavaMoabhu, navaAmoni, navaEdhomu, navaZidhoni, navaHiti; 2 vaiva vendudzi dzakanga dzanzi naJehovha kuvana vaIsiraeri, "Musaenda pakati pavo, naivo ngavarege kupinda pakati penyu; nokuti zvirokwazvo, vachatsautsa mwoyo yenyu mukazotevera vamwari vavo;" zvino Soromoni wakanamatira ivavo achivada. 3 Wakanga ana vakadzi vana mazana manomwe, vakunda vamadzimambo, navarongo vana mazana matatu; vakadzi vake vakatsautsa mwoyo wake. 4 Nokuti Soromoni wakati akwegura, vakadzi vake vakatsautsa mwoyo wake kuti atevere vamwe vamwari; mwoyo wake hauna kuzova wakarurama kwazvo kuna Jehovha Mwari wake, sezvakanga zvakaita mwoyo waDhavhidhi baba vake. 5 Nokuti Soromoni wakatevera Ashitoreti, mwarikadzi wavaZidhoni, naMirikomi mwari unonyangadza wavana vaAmoni. 6 Naizvozvo Soromoni wakaita zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha, haana kutevera Jehovha kwazvo, sezvakaita Dhavhidhi baba vake. 7 Zvino Soromoni akavakira Kemoshi, mwari unonyangadza waMoabhu, dunhu rakakwirira pagomo riri pamberi peJerusaremu; naMoreki, mwari unonyangadza wavana vaAmoni. 8 Saizvozvo akaitirawo vakadzi vake vose vatorwa, vaipisira vamwari vavo zvinonhuwira nokuvabayira. 9 Zvino Jehovha akatsamwira Soromoni, nokuti mwoyo wake wakatsauka kuna Jehovha Mwari walsiraeri, iye wakanga azviratidza kaviri kwaari, 10 akamuraira pamusoro pechinhu ichi, kuti arege kutevera vamwe vamwari; asi haana kuita zvaakanga arairwa naMwari. 11 Naizvozvo 3ehovha akati kuna Soromoni, "Zvawaita izvozvi, ukasachengeta sungano yangu nemitemo yangu, yandakakuraira, zvirokwazvo ndichabvarura ushe hwako, ndihubvise kwauri, ndihupe muranda wako. 12 Kunyange zvakadaro handingazviiti pamazuva ako nokuda kwaDhavhidhi baba vako; asi ndichahubvarura, ndikahubvisa paruoko rwomwanakomana wako. 13 Kunyange zvakadaro handingahwubvaruri ndikahubvisa hwose asi ndichapa mwanakomana wako rudzi rumwe nokuda kwaDhavhidhi muranda wangu, uye nokuda kweJerusaremu, iro guta randakatsaura." 14 Zvino Jehovha akamutsira Soromoni Hadhadhi muEdhomu, kuti arwe naye; iye wakanga ari worudzi rwamambo paEdhomu. 15 Nokuti panguva iya Dhavhidhi ari paEdhomu, Joabhu mukuru wehondo wakati akwira kundoviga vakanga vaurawa, apedza kuuraya varume vose paEdhomu; 16 (nokuti Joabhu navaIsiraeri vose vakagarapo mwedzi mitanhatu, kusvikira vaparadza varume vose paEdhomu;) 17 Hadhadhi akatiza, akaenda Ijipiti, iye navamwe vaEdhomu pakati pavaranda vababa vake, iye Hadhadhi achiri mwana muduku. 18 Ivo vakasimuka, vakabva Midhiani, vakasvika Parani; vakatora vamwe varume veParani, vakaenda Ijipiti kuna Farao mambo weIjipiti; iye akamupa imba, akaraira kuti apiwe zvokudya, akamupawo nyika pokugara. 19 Hadhadhi akazofarirwa kwazvo naFarao; naizvozvo akamupa muramu wake, munun'una wavahosi vake Tapenesi, ave mukadzi wake. 20 Munun'una waTapenesi akamuberekera mwanakomana wake Genubhati, wakarumurwa naTapenesi mumba maFarao; Genubhati akagara mumba maFarao, pakati pavanakomana vaFarao. 21 Zvino Hadhadhi wakati achinzwa kuti Dhavhidhi wavata namadzibaba ake, uye kuti Joabhu mukuru wehondo wafa, Hadhadhi akati kuna Farao, "Regai ndiende hangu kunyika yangu." 22 Farao akati kwaari, "Washaiweiko kwandiri, zvanoda kudzokera kunyika yako?" Akapindura, akati, "Handina kushaiwa chinhu; kunyange zvakadaro ndiregei henyu ndiende." 23 Zvino Jehovha akamumutsirazve mumwe kuzorwa naye, Rezonhi mwanakomana waEriadha, wakanga atiza kunashe wake Hadhadhezeri mambo weZo141a; akaunganidzira vanhu kwaari, akava mukuru wehondo panguva Dhavhidhi yaakauraya veZobha; vakaenda Dhamasiko, vakagarapo, vakabata ushe paDhamasiko. 25 Iye akarwa naIsiraeri mazuva ose aSoromoni, zvimwe zvakashata zvakaitwa naHadhadhi zvisingaverengwi iye akavenga vaIsiraeri, akabata ushe paSiria. 26 Jerobhoamuwo, mwanakomana waNebhati, muEfuremu weZeredha, muranda waSoromoni, zita ramai vake rainzi Zerua, yaiva chirikadzi, wakamukirawo mambo. 27 Iye wakamukira mambo nemhaka yokuti Soromoni wakanga avaka Miro, akagadzira pakanga pakaputsika paguta raDhavhidhi baba vake. 28 Zvino murume uyu Jerobhoamu wakanga ari murume wesimba noumhare, Soromoni akaona kuti jaya iro raibata kwazvo, akamuita mutariri wamabasa ose eimba yaJosefa. 29 Zvino panguva iyo Jerobhoamu wakati achibuda Jerusaremu, muporofita Ahija muShiro akasangana naye panzira; zvino Ahija wakanga akafuka nguo itsva; ivo vakanga vari vaviri voga kusango. 3Â° Ahija akabata nguo itsva yaakafuka, akaibvarura akaita mapande ane gumi namaviri. 31 Akati kuna Jerobhoamu, "Chizvitorera mapande ane gumi, nokuti zvanzi naJehovha, Mwari waIsiraeri, `Tarira, ndinobvarura ushe, ndihwubvise kuna Soromoni, ndikupe marudzi ane gumi. 32 (Asi iye uchava norudzi rumwe nokuda kwaDhavhidhi muranda wangu, uye nokuda kweJerusaremu, guta randakatsaura kumarudzi ose aIsiraeri;) 33 nokuti vakandirasha, vakanamata kuna Ashitoreti mwarikadzi wavaZidhoni, naKemoshi mwari wavaMoabhu, naMirikomi mwari wavana vaAmoni; havana kufamba panzira dzangu, nokuita zvakarurama pamberi pangu, nokuchengeta mitemo yangu nezvandakatonga, sezvakaita Dhavhidhi baba vake. 34 Kunyange zvakadaro handingabvisi ushe hwose paruoko rwake, asi ndichamuita muchinda mazuva ose oupenyu hwake nokuda kwaDhavhidhi muranda wangu, wandakatsaura; nokuti wakachengeta mirairo yangu nezvandakatema. 35 Asi ndichabvisa umambo kumwanakomana wake, ndihupe iwe, iwo marudzi ane gumi. 36 Asi mwanakomana wake ndichamupa rudzi rumwe, kuti Dhavhidhi muranda wangu ave nomwenje nguva dzose pamberi pangu paJerusaremu, iro guta randakazvitsaurira, ndiise zita
